response.original_title: Babad Tanah Leluhur II (Banyu Cakra Buana)
response.overview: Anting Wulan (Fitria Anwar) and Dampu Awuk (Gito Gilas), two martial arts masters, inform King Galuh that his son is  missing. Meanwhile, a minor uprising occurs and Anting Wulan and Dampu Awuk take action. Then a  contest is held to determine who will have the right to marry King Galuhâ€™s daughter, Nimas Kayuwangi (Devi Permata Sari). Anting Wulan wins the contest, but this somehow saddens him. There is no clear direction to this story, which appears to be little more than a vehicle for the fight scenes.
